This project is built on the shoulders of a considerable pile of open source work. Thank you to the authors and
maintainers of:

SCADA and HMI:
[Scada-LTS](https://github.com/SCADA-LTS/Scada-LTS)

Protocol simulators and gateways:
[Neuron](https://github.com/emqx/neuron) (EMQ Technologies),
